---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pomo Easy - Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Pomo Easy - Pomodoro Timer iOS app."
  ogUrl="https://idlefusion.com/pomo-easy/privacy"
>
  <main>
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-12">Pomo Easy - Pomodoro Timer &middot; Effective February 15, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
            <p>Pomo Easy does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. Everything stays on your device.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
            <p>All session data, timer settings, and statistics are stored locally on your device. No data is sent to any server, cloud service, or third party. There are no user accounts and no sign-up required.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">No HealthKit</h2>
            <p>Pomo Easy does not integrate with Apple HealthKit. Your focus sessions are not written to or read from Health data.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">No Accounts</h2>
            <p>There are no user accounts, no email collection, no sign-in, and no registration of any kind. You download the app and start using it immediately.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Analytics & Tracking</h2>
            <p>Pomo Easy contains no analytics frameworks, no ad SDKs, no tracking pixels, and no telemetry of any kind. We do not use any third-party services that collect data.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Network Usage</h2>
            <p>Pomo Easy makes no network requests. The app works entirely offline. The only network activity associated with the app is through the App Store for updates.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Focus Mode</h2>
            <p>If you enable Focus Mode integration, Pomo Easy uses iOS system APIs to activate your chosen Focus during work sessions. This happens entirely on-device and no data is transmitted.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>Pomo Easy does not knowingly collect any information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>If this policy changes, we will update this page with the new effective date. Since Pomo Easy collects no data, meaningful changes are unlikely.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
